# Rathole RDP - Slot Configuration
# Format: name|port|token|address|server
#
# name    : Unique identifier for this slot
# port    : Remote port on VPS (3389 = default RDP, no port needed in client)
# token   : Shared secret (generate with: openssl rand -hex 32)
# address : DNS name or IP for display (what you type in mstsc.exe)
# server  : VPS IP or hostname where rathole server runs
#
# Example:
# mypc|3389|a1b2c3d4e5f6...|mypc.example.com|203.0.113.1
# office|3390|f6e5d4c3b2a1...|office.example.com|203.0.113.1
